title: Trend Of The World As We Know It 1/22: Terry Jones, Earthquake, Vanessa Hudgens, Gritty, Britney Spears

description:
On this edition of It's the Trend of the World as we know it Miles and Blair Socci discuss Terry Jones passing away, the 3.6 Earthquake in Granda Hills, Vanessa Hudgens on a date with Kyle Kuzma, Gritty investigated for assault, and #FreeBritney is trending as she is in court.
